{
  "title": "Spicy Light Uruguayan Medjool Dates Stir-fry",
  "description": "This light and spicy medjool dates stir-fry is perfect for a brunch mood. It's egg-free-friendly, making it versatile for various dietary needs.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
  "diet": [
